' =============================================================================
' GTNH Platform — User Flow: Item, Fluid & Energy Transport
' 3 диаграммы: item pipes, fluid pipes, energy cables
' =============================================================================

' ===========================================================================
' 1. Item pipes (перемещение предметов между машинами)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml transport-item-pipes
title **Flow T1: Item Pipes (перемещение предметов)**

actor "SimulationCore\n(20 Hz Tick)" as Tick
participant "Machine A\n(output)" as A
participant "PipeNetwork" as PN
participant "Machine B\n(input)" as B
participant "ChunkStore" as CS

== Установка труб ==

Tick -> Tick: onBlockChanged: pipe placed
Tick -> PN: Notify pipe network update
PN -> PN: Rebuild graph (BFS)

== Каждый тик: выталкивание предмета ==

Tick -> A: tick(dt) — machine recipe complete
A -> A: Output slot has item

A -> PN: PushItemToPipe(output_slot, item, direction)

== PipeNetwork: BFS routing ==

PN -> PN: Find connected pipes from machine A output
PN -> PN: BFS to find valid input inventories
note right #5899DA
  BFS ищет:
  1. Соседние трубы (block_id in pipe list)
  2. Машины с input-слотом
  3. Фильтр: допустимый item для машины
end note

alt Connected machine B found
    PN -> B: Deliver item to input slot
    PN -> A: Confirm: item delivered
else No valid destination in network
    PN -> PN: Item stays in pipe buffer
    note right: Предмет ждёт в трубе,\nпока не появится получатель
end

== Перемещение предмета через цепочку труб ==

Tick -> Tick: Каждый тик: move items in pipes

loop Each pipe segment with items
    PN -> PN: Advance item one segment
    note right: Предмет движется по 1 блоку\nза тик (pipe speed)
    PN -> PN: Check next block

    alt Next is pipe
        PN -> PN: Move item to next pipe segment
    else Next is machine input
        PN -> PN: Insert into machine inventory

        alt Machine input full
            PN -> PN: Item stays, retry next tick
        end
    else Next is inventory/chest
        PN -> PN: Insert into chest inventory
    end
end

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 2. Fluid pipes (жидкости: вода, пар, нефть)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml transport-fluid-pipes
title **Flow T2: Fluid Pipes (жидкости)**

actor "SimulationCore\n(20 Hz Tick)" as Tick
participant "SteamBoiler" as Boiler
participant "PipeNetwork\n(fluid graph)" as PN
participant "SteamMachine" as Machine
participant "FluidTank\n(ECS component)" as Tank

== Fluids as items design decision ==

note right #5899DA
  Архитектурное решение:
  Жидкости = ItemStack (fluid item_id).
  FluidTank/FluidStack .fbs — для UI баков.
  PipeNetwork — отдельный граф для fluids.
  infinite source placeholder для воды.
end note

== Boiler -> PipeNetwork: подача пара ==

Tick -> Boiler: tick(dt)
Boiler -> Boiler: HEAT + water -> STEAM produced
Boiler -> PN: Publish fluid.node.update
note right: PipeNetwork обновляет\nfluid node state

== PipeNetwork -> Machine: распределение пара ==

Tick -> PN: tick(dt)
PN -> PN: BFS через fluid pipe graph
PN -> PN: Find connected fluid consumers

loop For each fluid consumer
    PN -> PN: Calculate distribution

    alt STEAM available in network
        PN -> Machine: Deliver steam amount
        PN -> PN: Deduct from source boiler
        Machine -> Machine: Advance recipe
    else No STEAM in network
        PN -> Machine: Steam insufficient
        Machine -> Machine: Idle (waiting for steam)
    end
end

== Fluids as items: рецепты ==

Tick -> Tick: RecipeManager проверяет input
note right #E67E22
  Рецепт может требовать:
  - item_id (обычный предмет)
  - fluid_id (как item_id)
  MachineInventory содержит
  fluid item_id в обычных слотах
end note

@enduml

' ===========================================================================
' 3. Energy cables (вольтаж, tier, потери, взрывы)
' ===========================================================================
@startuml transport-energy-cables
title **Flow T3: Energy Cables (вольтаж, tier, потери)**

actor "SimulationCore\n(20 Hz Tick)" as Tick
participant "Generator" as Gen
participant "PipeNetwork\n(energy graph)" as PN
participant "Machine" as Machine
participant "Cable" as Cable

== Generator -> Cable -> Machine ==

Tick -> Gen: tick(dt) — produce energy
Gen -> PN: Publish energy.node.update
note right: Generator tier: например MV (3),\nmaxOutput: 128 EU/t

== PipeNetwork: BFS распределение ==

Tick -> PN: tick(dt)
PN -> PN: BFS от generator через cables

loop For each cable segment
    PN -> Cable: GetCableTier(cable_pos)
    Cable --> PN: Tier (e.g. MV=3, max_voltage=128)

    PN -> PN: Check voltage match
    note right #E67E22
      Правила вольтажа:
      1. Cable tier >= generator tier -> OK
      2. Cable tier < generator tier:
         - Cable перегревается
         - Explosion если превышен лимит
      3. Cable tier > machine tier:
         - Machine может взорваться
         - Нужен transformer
    end note
end

== Energy distribution ==

PN -> PN: Find connected energy consumers
PN -> PN: Distribute available energy

loop For each consumer
    PN -> Machine: Deliver energy (tier-checked)
    Machine -> Machine: Advance recipe
    PN -> PN: Deduct from source

    alt Voltage mismatch
        PN -> PN: Overvoltage event
        PN -> PN: Cable segment destroyed
        PN -> CS: SetBlock CAS (AIR at cable pos)
    end
end

== Transformers: step up/down ==

Tick -> Tick: Transformer block placed
note right #438D80
  Transformer:
  - Step Up: MV->HV (128->512)
  - Step Down: HV->MV (512->128)
  - Sides: 1 face = high, 5 faces = low
  - Prevents explosions from tier mismatch
end note

@enduml
